# append(_:)

**Instance Method**

Appends an optional element to the column.

## Declaration

```swift
mutating func append(_ element: Any?)
```

## Parameters

- **element**: An element.

## Adding Elements

- **append(contentsOf:)**: Appends the contents of another column to the column.
- **append(contentsOf:)**: Appends the contents of a column slice to the column.
